OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMore people entertain at   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhome as living costs rise  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sales of home accessories and furniture
OL,6, rose sharply in March, as people ate   
OL,7, out less to save money and entertained 
OL,8, at home instead, new figures suggest.  
OL,10,FThe British Retail Consortium (BRC)    
OL,11,Fsaid this helped total retail sales    
OL,12,Fincrease by 5.1% last month compared   
OL,13,Fwith a year earlier.                   
OL,15,FIt comes as the cost of living remains 
OL,16,Fhigh, putting pressure on households.  
OL,18,FInflation - the rate at which prices   
OL,19,Fare rising - rose 10.4% in the year to 
OL,20,FFebruary.                              
